
--- Fuff ---

FFUF (Fuzz Faster U Fool) is a powerful and fast fuzzing tool used during web application penetration testing. Developed in the Go language, this tool can be used to rapidly test web directories, files, and parameter values for different types of fuzzing tests, revealing potential vulnerabilities.

• Features
